Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.25,0:01:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because of my match against\NIsumi-san yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't concentrate today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:51.44,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.17,0:01:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.07,0:01:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never going to play a match like yesterday,\Nor a match like today ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.06,0:02:02.95,Background,,0,0,0,,Was it because you were scared of Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So you got scared of him, and\Nmade a careless mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya... Isumi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,lost again today...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,against Fuku...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.69,0:02:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I'm disappointed. You're\Ntoo worried about Shindou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.05,0:02:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of regret ever seeing you as a rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Though thanks to all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:31.70,Background,,0,0,0,,Ochi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.70,0:02:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easier for me to pass undefea...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:47.15,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(315,115)}The Forty-First Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:47.15,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy70\fscx333\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}Three Weeks Isn't Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:01.17,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HC5FEC1&}He's coming in this deep?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:05.46,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HC5FEC1&}I'll be short on territory if he survives here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:09.84,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I won't let you survive that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:17.06,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Just you watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.65,0:03:32.39,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Ochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:34.76,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Though I respect your skill,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:37.82,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I never once thought that you were stronger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:09.69,Thinking,,0,0,0,,So that's what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:35.85,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san is back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:39.88,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:41.30,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:13.05,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Will that really do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:32.37,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Wow. He connected it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:45.64,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Now white's stones are all connected!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:50.61,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HC5FEC1&}I lost the fight on the right side!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:51.67,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HC5FEC1&}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:11.98,Memory,,0,0,0,,Shindou Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:13.56,Memory,,0,0,0,,My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.98,0:06:15.21,Memory,,0,0,0,,Shindou Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:17.74,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'm me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:25.13,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It's not that I lost confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:32.05,Thinking,,0,0,0,,My Go supports me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:12.93,Background,,0,0,0,,How did this part go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it. It went like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. Black lost the game there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:34.67,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Ochi. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:38.37,Thinking,,0,0,0,,You helped me get back on my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san, you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel as if I haven't seen you in days, Waya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that? What about Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The pro exam isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just starting, for both you and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:25.01,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HC5FEC1&}I don't know if Shindou is stronger than me or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:28.01,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HC5FEC1&}But, I'm still getting stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:31.15,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou isn't the only one that's getting stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:35.21,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I should believe in myself more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is it. I shouldn't have done\Na Hane when white did a Tsuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It would have been better if I\Nhad simply pulled back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,White would have had a harder\Ntime connecting then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it... that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ochi, find out for yourself how strong Shindou is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:37.07,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,360)}Ochi: 14 wins 1 loss
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:42.25,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,360)}Isumi: 12 wins 3 losses
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:47.33,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,360)}Waya: 13 wins 2 losses
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.84,0:10:52.84,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,360)}Shindou: 13 wins 2 losses
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:58.01,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,360)}Honda: 12 wins 3 losses
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:04.56,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(187,90)}Fukui: 8 wins 7 losses
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:04.56,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(455,360)}Nase: 8 wins 7 losses
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:09.17,Sai,,0,0,0,,Twelve matches left, we're\Nin the final stretch Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:10.19,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:20.92,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be playing you in the last round Ochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be much stronger than I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:49.69,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\frz348\move(283,93,277,83)}Japanese Go Research Center
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:49.69,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\fad(542,0)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,355)}Sixteenth Match of the Pro Exam Finals
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:52.50,Background,,0,0,0,,I resign...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:16.03,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Great, I managed to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:20.18,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I was scared of losing today, because\Nof the shock of losing to Isumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:26.38,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But Waya and Shindou won too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:28.69,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The same is true with Isumi-san and Honda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:33.06,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What if I mess up and fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:37.19,Thinking,,0,0,0,,No way. That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Iijima-san looked sad when he left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you won, Ochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing well too, staying at two losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:55.27,Background,,0,0,0,,You played Nase today right? Easy win?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:13:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're at an advantage, mistakes\Nhappen if you try to rush the win.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it's the pro exam, it's hard to play normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Being too determined to win\Ncan make you falter too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Emotions are difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:28.96,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou has changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:31.26,Thinking,,0,0,0,,And it's not just his strength in the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.63,0:13:35.74,Thinking,,0,0,0,,No, I can't be worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:42.93,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\fad(0,542)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,355)}Seventeenth Match of the Pro Exam Finals
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:47.16,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HC5FEC1&}Oh! Shindou lost to Honda-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:50.01,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Okay! Now Shindou has three losses!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:54.01,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I knew he'd start falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:57.49,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Honda-san has gone home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:13:59.48,Background,,0,0,0,,Oh, Honda-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You beat Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you, Isumi-san and Shindou\Nare all tied at three losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.79,0:14:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel relieved that Shindou lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's making such a fuss that\NShindou has gotten stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:17.86,Background,,0,0,0,,How was your game?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Honda-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I just barely won. No, I thought I had lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When we counted, I had half a moku left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I played well for myself, and I gained a lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I made the shape for a win. and\NI was determined not to budge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Shindou kept pushing\Nat me and pushing at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:53.58,Background,,0,0,0,,I tried to hold on, and the game ended\Njust when I thought I had lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There was half a moku left...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:15:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I can't believe that I won...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:11.34,Background,,0,0,0,,10...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:12.90,Background,,0,0,0,,20...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:16.85,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I dreamt that I was half a moku short.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:42.66,Sai,,0,0,0,,Is your loss from yesterday troubling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:48.28,Sai,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that you don't have a match today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can play, even if I have a match today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:01.79,Sai,,0,0,0,,His losses and his wins...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:07.30,Sai,,0,0,0,,All of the games leave something behind\Nin Hikaru, and make Hikaru stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:12.39,Sai,,0,0,0,,He grows with every game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:13.97,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa! Please call Touya 2dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best, in the three\Nweeks left of the pro exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please feel free to dress casually in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be excusing myself now, I have\Nsome work to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have someone bring you some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt you can do anything in just three weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But, grandpa told me to call you so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me "teacher" for the next three weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you listen to anyone\Nthat you're disrespectful to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You can call me "you" or "Touya" or anything\Nelse, after the pro exams are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You just said that I can't do anything\Nin only three weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. You won't get better\Njust by learning from a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I think I can help you in\Nyour match against Shindou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be taking advantage...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,of your obsession towards Shindou, teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to come every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:17:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I may not be able to come on some days\Nbecause of matches or my schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,On those days...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If I know about it in advance,\NI'll have another pro come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, replay Shuusaku's games.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuusaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there are around 400 of Shuusaku's\Ngames left on record.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:25.16,Background,,0,0,0,,Replay all of his games, as many times as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:28.21,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What does that have to do with Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:30.47,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HC5FEC1&}What is he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.06,0:18:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to show you this game first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:45.98,Background,,0,0,0,,A Korean kenkyuusei, Hong Su-Young, is black.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:49.46,Background,,0,0,0,,Shindou Hikaru is white.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou played a match against\Na Korean kenkyuusei!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A teacher from my junior high\Njust happened to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.92,0:19:05.49,Background,,0,0,0,,That teacher, replayed this game for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:33.67,Background,,0,0,0,,This... this white is Shindou!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That move that I thought was a mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,was actually preparing for the fight here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear that some of his Insei\Nfriends were there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:20:00.09,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It's Isumi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:03.59,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san saw this match.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:06.80,Thinking,,0,0,0,,That's why he was cautious against Shindou.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:10.27,Background,,0,0,0,,And in the end, white...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:13.59,Background,,0,0,0,,Shindou... wins by one and a half moku...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is really Shindou's strength right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Three weeks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm here for.
