Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kodaira Five's Go club is a brand new\Nclub that started just this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.58,0:22:36.23,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\q2\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad1\move(1535,360,-890,360)}Tokyo Kodaira Junior High School     Go club     Formed in 2002    9 Members       Formed by 7th graders who were inspired by Hikaru no Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.75,0:22:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, they played on home made Go boards.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.09,0:22:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But as you can see, they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.97,0:22:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,very active now. Doing things like...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.36,0:22:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,keeping records of their matches,\Nand solving problem sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.30,0:22:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I challenged a club member again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.14,0:22:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.72,0:22:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I was close to winning too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end, teacher Yukari gave us some Tsumego\Nproblems, and we solved them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.78,0:22:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Their club just started, but\Neveryone was really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.74,0:22:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost my game too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.34,0:22:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please keep up the good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HF50115&\4c&HF50115&\bord2\shad1\pos(250,328)}Everyone in Kodaira Junior High School
