Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H220DF2&\4c&H220DF2&\bord2\shad1\pos(508,455)}To be continued...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.33,0:22:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,460)}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.20,0:23:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The top five just won't fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.32,0:23:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally lost my grip on the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.45,0:23:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is Shindou!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.37,0:23:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I want to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.60,0:23:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to find out how strong Shindou\Nis. His mysterious strength.
